title: Total Finder v 1.1.11 + [K]racked
description:
Official Web Site: <a href=" http://totalfinder.binaryage.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://totalfinder.binaryage.com/</a>

Tabbed Browsing

Add tabs on top of Finder. The same tabs as seen in Google Chrome.

Show System Files

Show me all files on the disk.

Visor

Convenient system-wide Finder always one key-press away.

Folders on Top

Don't make me think. Folders should always go first in list view.

Cut & Paste

Use keyboard shortcuts to move files around. Faster than drag & drop.

Whats new: 

* NEW Localized into Belorussian by Alexander Shestakov.

* FIXED Fixed broken feature of dragging files to tabs (issue).

* FIXED Fixed invalid version info reported at some places (issue).

System Requirements:

Mac OS X.6
